definitions.definition: A domain or sphere that is part of a larger domain or sphere.
A domain name that has been prefaced with additional parts separated with periods .
An additional part prefaced to a domain name .
examples: In en.wiktionary.org , en is a subdomain .

main_definition: A domain or sphere that is part of a larger domain or sphere.
